Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:23.24,Main,,0,0,0,,瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:34.57,Main,,0,0,0,,不要走 不要走啊瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.38,Main,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:50.01,Main,,0,0,0,,瞬…
